log
@convert to new .Dd format;
@
text
@.\"	$OpenBSD: wdc.4,v 1.15 2007/01/29 21:29:47 martin Exp $
.\"	$NetBSD: wdc.4,v 1.4 1999/05/19 14:44:02 bouyer Exp $
